<p class="message">
  Hexagourds is a casual, relaxing 3D tile-placement game where you rotate and place tiles to make your own pumpkin patch.
  <font size="24"><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1778490/Hexagourds">Wishlist Hexagourds on Steam!</a></font>
</p>

<p><img src="https://media.githubusercontent.com/media/urodelagames/urodelagames.github.io/master/photos/HexagourdsMenu.gif" width="960" height="540" /></p>

<h3 id="what-do-you-do-in-hexagourds">What do you do in Hexagourds?</h3>
<ul>
  <li>You make a pumpkin patch!</li>
  <li>You gain tiles that have autumn-themed items that youâ€™d find at a pumpkin patch: Pumpkins, Haybales, Goats, etc.</li>
  <li>You place tiles on an empty grid that will become your own pumpkin patch.</li>
  <li>You get points along the way in different ways: Like making pumpkin combos and collecting apples from trees.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="how-can-i-follow-the-progress-for-hexagourds">How can I follow the progress for Hexagourds?</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Still in development, but you can follow my progress on <a href="https://twitter.com/urodelagames">Twitter</a>.</li>
  <li>I also have a new <a href="https://discord.gg/zMmxceBGkk">Discord server</a>.</li>
  <li>Iâ€™d love to have test/demo players help me decide on future features.</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="when-will-hexagourds-be-available">When will Hexagourds be available?</h3>
<ul>
  <li>You can play <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1778490/Hexagourds">the free demo on Steam</a> today!</li>
  <li>The full game will be released in January of 2022.</li>
</ul>

